trol room.<ref>{fr} {{cite web |url=http://www.asn.fr/sections/rubriquesprincipales/publications/rapport-annuel-asn/liste-rapports-annuels/2006/chapitre-12-centrales-nucleaires-d-8217/downloadFile/attachedFile_f0/RA-2006-Chapitre-XII-.pdf?nocache=1175506163.3 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2011-09-12 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929084324/http://www.asn.fr/sections/rubriquesprincipales/publications/rapport-annuel-asn/liste-rapports-annuels/2006/chapitre-12-centrales-nucleaires-d-8217/downloadFile/attachedFile_f0/RA-2006-Chapitre-XII-.pdf?nocache=1175506163.3 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |df= }}</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n{{stack|{{Portal|France|Energy|Nuclear technology}}}}\n* [[List of nuclear reactors#France|List of nuclear reactors - France]]\n\n== References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*{fr} [https://web.archive.org/web/20100526180846/http://energies.edf.com/edf-fr-accueil/la-production-d-electricite-edf/-nucleaire/les-centrales-nucleaires/saint-alban-120051.html Saint-Alban Power station website]\n\n{{French nuclear power plants}}\n\n[[Category:Nuclear power stations in France]]\n[[Category:Energy infrastructure completed in 1985]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Is\u00e8re]]\n\n[[no:Saint-Laurent kjernekraftverk]]\n", "name_user": "Quebec99", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fix duplicate ref names \u2013You can help!", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-Alban_Nuclear_Power_Plant"}
